---
import SiteLayout from '../../../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
import refactoringImg from '../../img/refactoring.jpg';
import legacyCodeImg from '../../img/legacy_code.jpg';
import { BASE_URL } from '../../../../../consts';

const indexList = [
  { id: '#pagetop', name: 'ページトップ' },
  { id: '#couplers', name: 'Couplers' },
  { id: '#featureenvy', name: 'Feature Envy' },
  { id: '#inappropriateintimacy', name: 'Inappropriate Intimacy' },
  { id: '#messagechains', name: 'Message Chains' },
  { id: '#middleman', name: 'Middle Man' }
];
---
<SiteLayout
  title="Couplers"
  description="Code Smell: Couplersの分類・参考情報をまとめたページです。"
  twitterCardSize="summary_large_image"
  indexList={indexList}
>
  <section class="box">
    <h2 class="title">Couplers</h2>
    <h2 id="couplers">Couplers</h2>
    <p><a href="https://sourcemaking.com/refactoring/smells/couplers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Couplers</a></p>
    <p>このグループのすべてのCode Smellは、クラス同士の結合度が高くなったり、結合を<a href="https://qiita.com/taumax/items/f192b16676f78fa04849#委譲delegate" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">委譲(delegate)</a>に置き換え過ぎた場合に何が起こるかを示しています。</p>
    <h1 id="featureenvy">Feature Envy</h1>
    <p><a href=`${BASE_URL}/contents/development/codesmell/category/sub_couplers/Feature_Envy`>Feature Envy（機能の横恋慕）</a></p>
    <h1 id="inappropriateintimacy">Inappropriate Intimacy</h1>
    <p><a href=`${BASE_URL}/contents/development/codesmell/category/sub_couplers/Inappropriate_Intimacy`>Inappropriate Intimacy（不適切な関係）</a></p>
    <h1 id="messagechains">Message Chains</h1>
    <p><a href=`${BASE_URL}/contents/development/codesmell/category/sub_couplers/Message_Chains`>Message Chains（メッセージの連鎖）</a></p>
    <h1 id="middleman">Middle Man</h1>
    <p><a href=`${BASE_URL}/contents/development/codesmell/category/sub_couplers/Middle_Man`>Middle Man（仲介人）</a></p>
    <br/><br/><br/>
    書籍としてはこの辺りが参考になると思います。<br/>
    <br/>
    リファクタリング第2版<br/>
  <a target="_blank" href="https://amzn.to/4m4SktG" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src={refactoringImg.src} alt="refactoring" /></a>
    <br/>
    レガシーコード改善ガイド<br/>
  <a target="_blank" href="https://amzn.to/44SixVn" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src={legacyCodeImg.src} alt="legacy_code" /></a>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
